c and can be applied atop LSTMs, Transformers, or Neural ODEs. Potential impact includes improved forecasting in domains like anomaly detection in IoT systems, ecological regime shifts, and high-frequency trading, where missing an extreme event is costlier than a false alarm. By integrating meta-learning, distributional awareness, and dynamic regret minimization, CDML moves beyond static imbalance correction toward truly adaptive intelligence in uncertain temporal environments.",
